'1355\t' + _x("npc conversation", "My brother, Elron, was an avid Arcomage player.  Have you played Arcomage yet?  Horribly addicting game, if I do say so.  In any rate, you can only play if you have a deck, and decks are hard to come by… so I guess you probably haven't.  In any case, Elron wanted to go over some strategies to help him win more games.  Unfortunately, he didn't want to be in town because he didn't want anyone else to spy on him learn his tricks so he went to the White Cliff Caves southeast a bit from town.\n\nElron hasn't been back in almost a week.  I'm certain something horrible has happened to him, but if he's alive I'd like to know that too.  Would you do me the service of locating him?  I don't have a lot of money to pay you back with, but I'd be greatly in your debt.") + '\tskill 280\t\r\n'
