'1370\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Knowing what you are up against in combat can mean the difference between life and death.  Being able to identify the monsters and opponents you are fighting can make this difference. I can teach you Expert Identify Monster if you already have a skill level of 4 and and pay 500 gold.") + '\tskill 296\t\r\n'
