'1390\t' + _x("npc conversation", "We have no one to turn to but you, the new Lords of Harmondale. The Lantern of Light is a treasured holy relic, used by the temples of Erathia.  Its value is more symbolic than of power-- without it the temples servants lose faith.  This Lantern disappeared while being brought to this temple from the temple in Stone City.  We believe it was lost somewhere in the maze-like Barrows.  Please find it and return it to us.") + '\tGet Lantern\t\r\n'
