'1393\t' + _x("npc conversation", "My, brother, Haldar passed away last month.  The family was sending his remains to me to be put to final rest.  Something happened to those delivering these remains to me; they disappeared in Nighon and not been heard from since. I fear my brothers soul will never rest unless they are found!  Please return Haldar to me if you find him? I will reward you well for this!") + "\tGet Haldar's Remains\t\r\n"
'1394\t' + _x("npc conversation", "Did you find Haldar's Remains?  His soul must be in sheer agony!  Please find the jar with his remains!") + "\tDon't have Haldar's Remains\t\r\n"
