'1699\t' + _x("npc conversation", "You did such a fine job with the Goblinwatch assignment that we would like to employ you again.  A cult has moved into an old abandoned temple a few day's journey west of here.  To pay for their blasphemous activities, they've been robbing travelers using the road that leads to Castle Ironfist.  We've appealed to the regent to do something about these horrible cultists, but he says all his forces are occupied in the west, or some such nonsense.  We want it gone now, so we're willing to pay you 5000 gold pieces to get rid of them and bring us back the Chime of Harmony as proof you've done the deed.") + '\t\t\r\n'
